Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.50,0:00:06.39,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}柳也
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.54,0:00:08.11,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}什麼事？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.52,0:00:13.71,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}我有事想拜託柳也
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.51,0:00:19.80,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}雖然還多少有些難為情
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.08,0:00:20.98,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}你能看一下嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.44,0:01:55.49,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}我開始了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.76,0:01:58.97,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.62,0:02:03.49,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}那是什麼東西？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.68,0:02:04.93,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}你看不出來嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.11,0:02:06.00,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}是手包啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.53,0:02:08.60,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}你到底打算幹什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.67,0:02:10.65,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}不是說過要拋手包嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.08,0:02:13.04,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}剛才還漂亮地拋起了三個呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.00,0:02:19.34,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}你不相信我嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.82,0:02:20.66,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}我說的是真的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.94,0:02:23.00,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}真的很漂亮地拋起了三個呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.00,0:02:23.72,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}晚安…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.85,0:02:24.98,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}別睡啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.26,0:02:26.58,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}你快回去睡吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.84,0:02:28.19,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}我還在放哨呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.61,0:02:31.55,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}主人要給你看拿手絕活呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.84,0:02:35.73,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}做臣子的不是該跪下恭恭敬敬地拜見嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.75,0:02:36.90,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}別胡攪蠻纏了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.13,0:02:38.97,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}好  我命令你
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.17,0:02:40.49,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}啊  等等！ 等等！ 等等！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.64,0:02:45.23,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}別在這種時候用主人的命令來壓我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.55,0:02:48.30,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}我可不想再立什麼多餘的誓言了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.40,0:02:52.90,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}疼疼疼疼疼…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.73,0:02:54.82,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}別咬人啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.08,0:02:58.07,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}還不怪你自己太粗暴了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.44,0:03:03.49,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.91,0:03:06.49,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}我看著就是了  你快點拋吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.88,0:03:08.87,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}你說的話… 總是這麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.93,0:03:10.38,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}知道了知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.40,0:03:10.98,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}我想看
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.28,0:03:14.34,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}我想看想得不得了  你快點拋吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.79,0:03:16.97,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}還是那麼一點誠意也沒有啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.18,0:03:18.87,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.20,0:03:22.09,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}看過我的絕技之後  你的態度也就會變了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.23,0:03:27.25,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}我終於找到竅門了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.71,0:03:30.98,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}哼  學會了之後就是這麼簡單的事情啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.31,0:03:34.42,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}現在  我已經是不輸給裏葉的手包名人了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.80,0:03:41.30,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}我終於明白  全心全意去學習一件事物是多麼地重要了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.46,0:03:43.04,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.96,0:03:58.83,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}剛才那絕對是搞錯了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.00,0:04:18.28,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}我沒說謊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.61,0:04:20.44,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}真的已經學會了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.19,0:04:24.10,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}誰也沒說你說謊啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.39,0:04:26.80,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}我看著呢  你儘管拋吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.10,0:04:28.43,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}這次一定要…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.77,0:04:29.94,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}肩膀放鬆一些嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.31,0:04:32.88,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}不放鬆一些的話  名人也做不好的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.22,0:04:34.35,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}是… 是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.24,0:04:40.06,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}我要開始了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.41,0:04:43.76,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}怎麼樣  怎麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.95,0:04:45.14,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}我拋得不錯吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.34,0:04:51.44,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}能做到這樣已經很了不起了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.13,0:04:53.45,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}用不著安慰我的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.79,0:04:54.82,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}這不是安慰
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.13,0:04:58.37,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}能做成這樣  是因為你努力練習了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.65,0:05:01.05,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}不懂得放棄可真是了不起啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.42,0:05:04.61,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}聽不懂你到底是在誇我還是在嘲笑我
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.93,0:05:06.02,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}是在誇你呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.89,0:05:09.32,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}不管怎麼說  你幹得很好  神奈
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.79,0:05:11.58,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}我還想做得更好
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.93,0:05:14.47,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}每天都練習的話肯定會變得很拿手的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.14,0:05:16.10,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}真誇張
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.41,0:05:17.48,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}真的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.46,0:05:22.08,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}你還會再看我拋手包嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.18,0:05:25.12,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}嗯  只要你願意
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.54,0:05:28.56,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}趁現在快去睡一會吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.85,0:05:29.74,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}今天還要走很多路呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.12,0:05:30.73,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.60,0:05:48.62,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}看來必須越過這些群山峻嶺才行了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.09,0:05:54.79,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}想逃脫追兵的話  在山林裏行進是再好不過的了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.47,0:05:57.07,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}我去取些水來
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.97,0:06:06.11,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}怎麼了  神奈
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.35,0:06:14.09,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}疼…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.10,0:06:20.68,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}求你饒了我吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.16,0:06:24.40,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}進不去了… 都說過進不去了…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.59,0:06:26.60,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}饒了我吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.36,0:06:30.94,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}我已經…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.67,0:06:34.01,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}已經吃不下去了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.69,0:06:39.25,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}喂  這麼睡的話會感冒的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.07,0:06:54.98,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}喂  別再睡第二覺了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.59,0:07:00.90,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}也別睡第三覺了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.55,0:07:03.49,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}柳也大人  您太手軟了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.00,0:07:16.73,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}很疼的啊  你幹什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.75,0:07:20.11,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}神奈大人  您感覺好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.45,0:07:22.81,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}你看我像感覺好的樣子嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.23,0:07:25.63,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}叫我起床時就不能再溫柔些嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.91,0:07:29.38,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}那麼下次我就再注意一下力度…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.43,0:07:32.45,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}我是讓你別再抽枕頭了！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.43,0:07:43.92,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}你的耳朵可真奇怪啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.29,0:07:47.18,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}跑起來的話不會刮到草木上去嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.55,0:07:51.66,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}耳朵這麼長的話  可以聽得很遠吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.35,0:08:00.86,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}可惡  居然敢耍我
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.18,0:08:02.15,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}喂  給我停下
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.38,0:08:04.08,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}給我停下啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.37,0:08:06.06,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}喂！ 停下停下停下停下！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.27,0:08:07.58,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}啊  吵死了！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.84,0:08:09.12,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}給我安靜一點
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.08,0:08:14.00,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}你一直在看什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.26,0:08:16.22,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}前幾天在集市上找到的地圖
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.51,0:08:17.77,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}很珍貴的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.67,0:08:21.49,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}這些像蟲子一樣的東西是什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.70,0:08:22.44,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}是河流的名字
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.02,0:08:25.19,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}神奈  你不認識字嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.77,0:08:27.44,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}沒有人教我
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.72,0:08:29.38,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}又怎麼可能認識呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.73,0:08:31.29,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}裏葉居然也不管你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.89,0:08:33.32,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}我才沒有不管呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.63,0:08:38.99,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}因為神奈大人說過「絕對不想跟裏葉學字」…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.37,0:08:41.19,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}那不是要怪裏葉嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.42,0:08:43.76,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}該不會忘了歌集那件事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.04,0:08:47.48,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}那是為了豐富神奈大人的心靈才…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.73,0:08:50.18,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}靠你那種教人的方法  心靈怎麼會豐富得起來
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.48,0:08:51.55,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}你們在說什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.79,0:08:56.72,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}以前  我曾經教過神奈大人背誦和歌
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.08,0:09:00.00,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}學習東西當然要付出一點點心血了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.27,0:09:02.59,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}可是神奈大人卻…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.03,0:09:07.17,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}一天要背二百首  還叫什麼「一點點心血」啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.47,0:09:09.69,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}一共有四千五百首呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.94,0:09:11.46,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}磨磨蹭蹭怎麼行呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.33,0:09:15.31,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}我已經五天沒睡了…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.70,0:09:20.52,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}還剩下二百首  再忍耐一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.54,0:09:23.83,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}你的命還真大啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.53,0:09:25.39,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.68,0:09:27.95,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}我想這樣下去肯定會死掉的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.29,0:09:31.08,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}所以把歌集全都扔到爐灶裏去了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.43,0:09:35.72,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}寶貴的古今六帖一併全都變成早飯的柴火了…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.33,0:09:40.56,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}那天的飯  真是充滿了風流的味道啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.30,0:09:45.21,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}就是這張嘴在胡說八道嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.74,0:09:47.14,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}快放開… 裏葉…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.25,0:09:50.82,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}連一首和歌也唱不出來的嘴巴  根本就是沒用的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.31,0:09:52.56,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}太沒道理了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.82,0:09:54.67,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}我乾脆把它縫上算了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.54,0:09:56.61,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}你還在幹什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.94,0:09:58.94,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}快救救我
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.63,0:10:02.35,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}可是  我也怕裏葉啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.06,0:10:04.98,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}你這沒用的傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.31,0:10:11.10,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}對不起  我有些太激動了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.16,0:10:12.96,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}不用在意
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.13,0:10:14.79,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}為什麼你要原諒她啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.09,0:10:16.21,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}你的聲音還是很怪啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.63,0:10:18.30,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}啊  夠了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.18,0:10:21.38,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}我到那邊去練習拋手包了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.73,0:10:23.69,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}在這裏待著心會亂的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.01,0:10:26.60,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}那我也陪你一起去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.86,0:10:28.37,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}用不著你陪
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.11,0:10:34.82,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}為什麼要打我
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.01,0:10:37.41,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}我在亂發脾氣
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.47,0:10:44.50,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}神奈  怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.13,0:11:03.77,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}是和尚嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.52,0:11:05.47,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}身上沒有傷
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.73,0:11:07.24,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}看來是累倒的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.76,0:11:22.75,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}柳也
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.99,0:11:26.49,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}能說一會話嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.94,0:11:27.64,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}什麼事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.86,0:11:28.67,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}又要拋手包嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.53,0:11:30.54,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}不是的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.53,0:11:34.87,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}你是不是有什麼心事呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.10,0:11:37.07,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}心事？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.29,0:11:37.93,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.26,0:11:42.15,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}有什麼想說的話不必憋在心裏  把它說出來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.42,0:11:43.66,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}想說的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.04,0:11:48.87,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}那我就說一句好了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.09,0:11:50.10,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}嗯  什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.78,0:11:52.43,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}你的頭頂上有只毛毛蟲
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.87,0:12:00.31,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}你好像很容易吸引野獸和蟲子之類的東西啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.74,0:12:02.94,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}別那麼冷靜啊  就不能救救我嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.39,0:12:06.78,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}剛才就一直覺得你很古怪
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.22,0:12:09.60,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}本來想作為主人關心一下臣子來著
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.81,0:12:11.36,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}結果弄得自己這麼沒面子
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.46,0:12:14.87,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}抱歉  我說給你聽就是了  別走啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.26,0:12:18.18,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}不會再拿我開玩笑了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.61,0:12:21.44,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}這可是很無聊的事情哦  你真的想聽嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.77,0:12:23.10,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}你儘管說吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.04,0:12:27.92,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}我沒見過自己的父母
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.05,0:12:29.86,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}為什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.80,0:12:32.61,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}大概  是被扔掉了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.98,0:12:36.09,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}在路邊哭泣的時候  被行腳僧撿到了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.32,0:12:39.31,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}行腳僧就是旅行的和尚
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.68,0:12:43.66,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}所謂的行腳僧聽起來似乎很不錯
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.02,0:12:47.66,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}其實也只是無家可歸  四處乞討的人而已
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.52,0:12:52.34,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}我們倆一起周遊了各種各樣的土地
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.25,0:12:56.52,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}北方 南方 東方 西方  去過各種各樣的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.46,0:13:00.87,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}他是柳也的養育之親嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.21,0:13:03.14,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}也算不上是什麼養育之親
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.64,0:13:08.49,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}他是個嚴厲的人  除了誦經之外從不開口說閒話
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.38,0:13:11.85,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}就連法名最終也沒有告訴我
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.40,0:13:16.33,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}在大約五歲時的夏天
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.05,0:13:23.94,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}我們在山路上遇到了山賊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.43,0:13:26.28,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}行腳僧被一刀殺死了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.09,0:13:29.62,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}看到剛才那個和尚
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.94,0:13:31.75,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}我想起了這件事
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.41,0:13:36.35,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}原來柳也也沒有母親嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.89,0:13:42.39,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}可是  我卻只顧追尋自己的母親
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.17,0:13:44.13,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}不用在意
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.50,0:13:46.29,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}這也是我的希望
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.36,0:13:52.28,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}那個行腳僧臨死前還在祈禱
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.93,0:13:56.02,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}祝願殺死自己的人能夠往升淨土
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.09,0:14:00.33,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}之後  自己死在了血泊中
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.54,0:14:02.81,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}我沒有被殺
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.30,0:14:07.04,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}他們說我不值得弄髒他們的刀
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.22,0:14:11.28,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}就這樣  我又獨自一人站在路邊了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.74,0:14:19.08,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}那以後  我一直都是一個人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.01,0:14:22.18,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}為了活下去  我什麼都幹過
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.95,0:14:25.23,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}偷走過別人的刀槍  參加過戰爭
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.89,0:14:27.05,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}也殺過人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.70,0:14:30.35,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}每天都只想著自己如何才能活下去
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.75,0:14:34.26,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}直到最近為止
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.40,0:14:35.20,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}最近…？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.31,0:14:36.35,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}最近發生過什麼嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.23,0:14:41.06,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}這就是所謂的心境轉變
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.68,0:14:44.35,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}只要有一些契機  人都會改變的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.33,0:14:49.18,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}那些山賊一定也很後悔吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.40,0:14:53.06,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}他們殺了一位德高望重的高僧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.29,0:14:54.72,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}當然會後悔吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.82,0:14:58.61,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}很難說他能不能算得上是德高望重的高僧啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.94,0:15:00.75,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}你在懷疑什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.14,0:15:03.61,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}正是因為聽到了行腳僧的祈禱
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.88,0:15:07.28,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}山賊們才沒有殺害柳也吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.13,0:15:15.08,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}是嗎…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.20,0:15:19.94,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}那個時候  我或許確實是被行腳僧救了一條命呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.94,0:15:23.45,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}為什麼沒有早點注意到這一點呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.89,0:15:26.38,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}那樣的話  我就一定會走上另一條道路了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.66,0:15:27.91,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}那可不行
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.40,0:15:31.47,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}那樣的話  我不是就遇不到柳也了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.71,0:15:32.76,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.39,0:15:35.87,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}我也慶幸自己能遇到神奈
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.13,0:15:39.20,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}柳也
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.68,0:15:43.89,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}柳也
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.97,0:15:46.48,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.19,0:15:48.09,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.27,0:15:48.95,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.47,0:15:52.76,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}我不知道接下來該怎麼做才好…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.34,0:15:56.32,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}所以…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.79,0:15:59.58,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}後邊的事就拜託給柳也了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.13,0:16:11.54,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}我很難為情的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.84,0:16:12.78,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}快點啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.57,0:16:14.20,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}我說啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.48,0:16:17.77,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}你真的知道接下來要幹什麼嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.53,0:16:20.12,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}別… 別小看我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.35,0:16:21.60,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}我很清楚的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.88,0:16:23.80,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}裏葉全都教給我了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.35,0:16:26.41,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}果然是裏葉搗的鬼嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.05,0:16:27.94,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.14,0:16:30.31,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}柳也對我來說就是…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.63,0:16:32.17,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}雖然說不清楚…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.74,0:16:34.65,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}但是… 那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.55,0:16:39.10,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}裏葉說過
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.76,0:16:44.36,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}「柳也說起往事的時候  就別放過那個機會」
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.82,0:16:50.18,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}男性是一定會對喜歡的女性說起往事來的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.87,0:16:52.37,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}她是這麼說的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.36,0:16:54.92,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}都被她猜中了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.38,0:16:59.42,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}「聽柳也說完後  就慢慢地解開衣服」
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.04,0:17:04.17,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}她還說過什麼「需要讓胸部若隱若現」之類的話
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.76,0:17:06.82,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}連導演都做好了嗎…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.62,0:17:09.70,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}我弄錯什麼了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.80,0:17:15.06,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}莫非  柳也只喜歡男色嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.39,0:17:16.33,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.72,0:17:17.78,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}哦  對了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.01,0:17:21.17,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}有些男性雖然喜歡女性  卻很無能
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.73,0:17:23.62,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}別胡說八道了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.72,0:17:26.97,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}果然還是因為把衣服脫得過頭了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.60,0:17:28.62,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}好  我明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.26,0:17:33.66,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}我就讓你知道我也是個男人  你做好準備吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.20,0:17:36.98,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}柳也  你的眼神很怪啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.27,0:17:39.08,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}是你來引誘我的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.37,0:17:41.16,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}就老老實實讓我用毒牙咬一口吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.64,0:17:43.79,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}柳… 柳也有毒的嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.07,0:17:45.72,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}男人全都是有毒的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.00,0:17:49.10,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}而且還有更多你不知道的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.53,0:17:53.63,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}就讓我一步一步教你好了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.94,0:17:56.29,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}喂  快住手！ 住手！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.99,0:17:58.53,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}住手！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.97,0:18:02.79,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}裏葉  你藏在那裏吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.02,0:18:03.52,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}給我出來
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.48,0:18:08.37,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}你依然是那麼精明呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.44,0:18:17.00,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}神奈大人  您沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.37,0:18:20.25,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}不太清楚… 不過似乎不太成功…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.16,0:18:21.91,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}柳也…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.61,0:18:26.36,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}我惹柳也生氣了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.02,0:18:28.71,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}我沒生氣
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.71,0:18:33.63,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}裏葉
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.90,0:18:36.86,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}你是不是看穿我絕對不會出手的了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.19,0:18:39.33,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}其實我自己也不是很確定
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.75,0:18:42.31,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}天下哪還有我這種人畜無害的男人了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.62,0:18:44.68,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}也可以說是無能呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.86,0:18:45.89,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}囉嗦！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.61,0:18:54.92,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}她睡得很香嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.89,0:18:59.60,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}今天也熱心地做過手包的修煉呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.38,0:19:04.15,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}睡著的時候  倒是很可愛的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.57,0:19:06.39,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}在無聊男人們聚過來之前
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.62,0:19:09.07,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}得教會她色戀之事才行啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.48,0:19:10.75,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}別用我來練習啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.59,0:19:13.15,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}她還是個孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.49,0:19:17.01,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}連人偶和手包都沒有玩過呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.74,0:19:20.78,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}母親大人…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.15,0:19:23.85,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}您醒了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.63,0:19:28.24,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}我做了一個夢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.70,0:19:31.77,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}是一個在其他地方的夢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.23,0:19:36.15,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}我穿著奇特的衣裝  相貌也改變了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.10,0:19:39.89,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}那真的是我嗎…？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.98,0:19:42.61,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}變成什麼樣的相貌了呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.28,0:19:44.86,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}記不清楚了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.20,0:19:47.53,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}不過  身邊有我的母親
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.05,0:19:50.33,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}還有很多善良的人們
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.95,0:19:53.60,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}我非常地幸福
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.98,0:19:57.16,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}是個很好的夢呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.90,0:20:00.34,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}只要把這個夢變成現實不就行了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.77,0:20:02.82,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}你馬上就能見到母親了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.61,0:20:06.11,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}那時候  你的夢就不再是夢了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.49,0:20:07.56,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.94,0:20:11.97,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}只要虔誠祈禱  上天就一定能夠聽到我的心意
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.16,0:20:25.49,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}看啊  看啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.77,0:20:27.01,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}我做得很好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.99,0:20:28.81,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}它們沒有掉下來
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.73,0:20:30.83,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}一個也沒有掉下來
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.65,0:20:50.07,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}看來還需要再修煉一段時間啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.84,0:20:53.79,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}不過  真的是很棒啊  神奈大人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.22,0:20:58.20,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}只要繼續修煉下去  一定會更加出色的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.70,0:20:59.63,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}真的嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.15,0:21:03.21,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}到時候我就可以做給母親看了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.52,0:21:04.76,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}當然了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.10,0:21:17.60,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}我們該走了  神奈
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.55,0:21:22.18,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}怎麼了  不和我一起來嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.05,0:21:35.78,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}那是你的母親嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.44,0:21:38.34,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.59,0:21:48.83,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}要永遠幸福地生活下去啊
